Dialogue: 1,0:10:41.35,0:10:43.57,720PCN,,0,0,0,,核动力引擎的效率能
Dialogue: 2,0:10:41.35,0:10:43.57,720PEN,,0,0,0,,The efficiency of the nuclear engines would
