Dialogue: 2,0:10:43.86,0:10:47.94,720PEN,,0,0,0,,enable a trip to Mars in a hundred days not quite as quickly as were proposed
Dialogue: 1,0:10:47.94,0:10:52.52,720PCN,,0,0,0,,毛子的发动机快，但相比传统化学火箭已经是很大的进步了
