Dialogue: 1,0:10:52.52,0:10:58.80,720PCN,,0,0,0,,同时“哥白尼”号的反应堆也是支持双模式的
Dialogue: 2,0:10:52.52,0:10:58.80,720PEN,,0,0,0,,engines and also Copernicus would be capable of bimodal reactor operation.
